data.description: SO MUCH SPACE plus a LARGE CORNER LOT! With over 2,000 sq ft, this spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom craftsman style home is a timeless gem, complete with beautiful decorative fireplaces, high ceilings, pocket doors, and an ideal CORNER LOT location. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the high ceilings that create an open and inviting atmosphere from the start. The main floor features a spacious living area that flows seamlessly into the dining room, perfect for family gatherings or entertaining guests. The laundry room is located off the kitchen, which boasts modern conveniences while preserving the home's character. 3 bedrooms provide spacious retreats while the 4th would be great as an office or nursery. The two bathrooms are tastefully updated, ensuring your daily routines are a breeze. Crafton offers a small-town charm while being just a stone's throw away from the city. Enjoy proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment options. It's the perfect place to call home!
